We have recommended that Management:

Conduct a complete physical inventory of the Land Improvement projects implemented by the LGU; 

Reconcile the Land improvement account with the Physical Inventory Report and the reports   of the Accounting Unit;

Update the PPE Ledger Cards of the Municipal Accounting Unit on the Land Improvement account; and 

Ensure that the corresponding Accumulated Depreciation account is also adjusted accordingly.

