establish cut-off period for the remittance of CTCs for deputized barangay collectors;
observe the practice of remitting all collections daily and deposit them with the depository bank daily or not later than the next banking day or as often as practicable subject to health restrictions due to pandemic; and
optimally use the RAAF in monitoring the receipt, issuance, and balances of accountable forms.

