submit the contract and purchase orders complete with supporting documents within five working days upon execution thereof;
in coordination with the BAC to submit the deficient documents and review the noted deficiencies mentioned under item 6.26 of this Memorandum; and
require the OIC-Municipal Accountant to determine appropriate asset accounts to record the purchased equipment.

