preparation of Project Procurement Management Plan (PPMP) as basis for the preparation of the Annual Procurement Plan (APP);
on future similar undertakings on infrastructure projects, conduct complete detailed engineering prior to the preparation of bid documents in order to assure the viability of infrastructure project;
