(a)  coordinate efforts with the barangay officials on the implementation of the five basic environmental laws on preserving and protecting the environment required under R.A. No. 9003;  

(b) request the Municipal Solid Waste Management Board to prioritize the finalization of the ten-year SWMP for the early identification of issues/gaps in complying with RA No. 9003 and the prompt resolution thereof;  

(c) enforce the Sangguniang Bayan ordinance on the “no segregation, no collection” policy; and       

(d) initiate intensive information drive and awareness campaign on the regulations on solid waste management in coordination with barangay officials.

